OL,3,CNew Tyne and Wear Metro trains pulled
OL,4,Cfrom service
OL,6,FA total of 46 trains have been ordered
OL,7,Fand are due to be rolled out gradually
OL,8,Fbefore the end of 2026.
OL,10,FThey will replace the current fleet,
OL,11,Fwhich has been in service since the
OL,12,Fnetwork opened in 1980 and have become
OL,13,Fincreasingly unreliable.
