OL,3,CNew Tyne and Wear Metro trains pulled
OL,4,Cfrom service
OL,6,FCathy Massarella, Managing Director of
OL,7,FNexus, said: "We have recently
OL,8,Fidentified an operational issue with
OL,9,Fthe new Metro trains which is
OL,10,Faffecting the dispatch process with
OL,11,Fthe doors. We have therefore decided
OL,12,Fto temporarily pause the new fleet's
OL,13,Fentry into customer service while we
OL,14,Finvestigate this further.
OL,16,F"The introduction of a new fleet of
OL,17,Ftrains is very complex and we would
OL,18,Fexpect to see minor technical and
OL,19,Foperational issues crop up as part of
OL,20,Fthis process.
OL,26,@oD@NOUxD@AOU
