OL,3,CNew Tyne and Wear Metro trains pulled
OL,4,Cfrom service
OL,6,F"The roll out is a mix of continued
OL,7,Ftechnical performance monitoring,
OL,8,Ftweaking operational practices, and
OL,9,Funderstanding how customers are
OL,10,Finteracting with the range of new
OL,11,Ffeatures of the train.
OL,13,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,14,FStadler to review and address any
OL,15,Fissues, and continually learn from
OL,16,Fthem. This is why we have taken a
OL,17,Fcareful phased approach to fleet
OL,18,Fintroduction.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
