OL,3,CNew Tyne and Wear Metro trains pulled
OL,4,Cfrom service
OL,6,F"Thankfully these trains benefit from
OL,7,Fa really sophisticated diagnostic
OL,8,Fsystem so when anything unexpected
OL,9,Fdoes arise, it is usually identified
OL,10,Fquickly. This minimises disruption to
OL,11,Fservices and gives us valuable
OL,12,Flearning to address future reliability.
OL,14,F"We are aiming to continue with the
OL,15,Froll out of the new fleet as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible. We will keep customers
OL,17,Fupdated and I'd like to thank them in
OL,18,Fadvance for their patience."
